{"tid":2387412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國產首座第3代核電「華龍一號」　正式投入商業運行","createTime":"2021-01-30T09:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T11:46:22.000Z","uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4696c58c2e9d8c1630ffabe805bf27305684f107","tid":2387412,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"華龍<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210130/photo/bkn-20210130150821779-0130_00952_001_01p.jpg?20210130152606\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210130150821779-0130_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20210130152606&h=a2ff087f&s={SIZE}\" />一號福清核電5號機組。<br />\n國產首座第3代核電「華龍一號」福清核電5號機組，周六（30日）已通過連續運行測試，正式投入商業運行。研發方中核集團表示，這標誌着中國成為繼美國、法國、俄羅斯等國後，真正掌握自主三代核電技術的國家，核電技術躋身世界前列。<br />\n中核集團黨組書記、董事長余劍鋒介紹，華龍一號是當前世界核電市場上接受度最高的三代核電機型之一，其設計壽命60年，反應堆採用177堆芯設計，堆芯設計換料週期18個月，採用雙層安全殼等技術，所有設備國產化率達88%，當局已完全具備批量生產該機型的能力。<br />\n據指出，華龍一號每台機組每年可發電近100億千瓦時，能滿足中等發達國家100萬人口的生產和生活年度用電需求，同時相當於減少標準煤消耗312萬噸、減少二氧化碳排放816萬噸，對優化中國能源結構、推動綠色低碳發展、助力碳達峰、實現碳中和目標具有重要意義。"},{"pid":"b9c96903f779c4ab383fc6d8df658c0143ee0da6","tid":2387412,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"抄法國嘢抄咗幾十年終於畢業"},{"pid":"979d6319993c0dd44f9dc082fb10a144d1eba7dd","tid":2387412,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"核災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf60663b27b927eaeab8020a3ce8724aad1f2e6","tid":2387412,"uid":167394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9c96903f779c4ab383fc6d8df658c0143ee0da6","tid":2387412,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"抄法國嘢抄咗幾十年終於畢業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"法國抵死"},{"pid":"d25e200f553679d93f49ab6cead42fb861ada9b5","tid":2387412,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"支那研制會爆的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be20f1b9eec8f946ce526bfaef5f173fa2ec80b","tid":2387412,"uid":189430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"華龍一號每台機組每年可發電近100億千瓦時，能滿足中等發達國家100萬人口的生產和生活年度用電需求，同時相當於減少標準煤消耗312萬噸、減少二氧化碳排放816萬噸，對優化中國能源結構、推動綠色低碳發展、助力碳達峰、實現碳中和目標具有重要意義。<br />\n<br />\n必要時仲可以自爆,減少低端人口"},{"pid":"6514800d950a2b523c2d7b9b162c828350d5a1a5","tid":2387412,"uid":265318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"起左喺邊呀大佬？<br />\n方圓三百公里劃定exclusion zone"},{"pid":"209f1f9017692cf2e059c481f9d10f36e09b6353","tid":2387412,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6514800d950a2b523c2d7b9b162c828350d5a1a5","tid":2387412,"uid":265318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"起左喺邊呀大佬？<br />\n方圓三百公里劃定exclusion zone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"福建福清市"},{"pid":"a265bb49dc94bccb1318bebbe0b12060f7e120d7","tid":2387412,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209f1f9017692cf2e059c481f9d10f36e09b6353","tid":2387412,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6514800d950a2b523c2d7b9b162c828350d5a1a5","tid":2387412,"uid":265318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"起左喺邊呀大佬？<br />\n方圓三百公里劃定exclusion zone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"福建福清市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"福建人有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4ed09b70ec298083ec3a7d639e1dc6fc1a53ca","tid":2387412,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"979d6319993c0dd44f9dc082fb10a144d1eba7dd","tid":2387412,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"核災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji